The best pattern here is to keep the page as a Server Component for data fetching and use `Link` components for navigation. The only `useRouter` usage is a button that navigates to `/blog` - this can be replaced with a `Link` or... wait, it calls `router.push('/blog')` in a click handler. In App Router with Server Components, I should convert this to use `Link` from `next/link`.

