### 4. `app/blog/[id]/page.tsx` (replaces `pages/blog/[id].js`)

This is more complex:
- `getStaticPaths` → `generateStaticParams`
- `getStaticProps` → Server Component data fetching
- `router.isFallback` → `loading.tsx` pattern (create `app/blog/[id]/loading.tsx`)
